FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our adorable Kitten Mittens
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Kitten Mittens are adorable, paw-fect accessories designed to keep your feline friend's paws warm and stylish. They're the cat's meow in fashion and comfort!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I measure my kitten for mittens?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Gently place your kitten's paw on a piece of paper and trace around it. Measure the width and length, then consult our size guide for the purrfect fit.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Are Kitten Mittens safe for my cat?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Our Kitten Mittens are made with soft, non-toxic materials and designed for your cat's comfort and safety. Always supervise your kitten while they're wearing their mittens.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can Kitten Mittens be worn outdoors?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: While Kitten Mittens are primarily designed for indoor use, they can be worn for short outdoor adventures. Just make sure to keep an eye on your fashionable feline!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Do you offer a satisfaction guarantee?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes! We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If your kitten isn't totally in love with their mittens, we'll refund your purchase. Your cat's happiness is our top priority!
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Kitten Mittens
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Kitten Mittens are adorable, paw-shaped mittens designed specifically for cats. They provide warmth, protection, and a touch of whimsy to your feline friend's paws.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How do I measure my cat's paws for Kitten Mittens?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: To measure your cat's paws, gently press their paw onto a piece of paper and trace around it. Measure the width and length, then refer to our size guide to find the perfect fit.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Are Kitten Mittens safe for cats?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, Kitten Mittens are made with cat-safe materials and designed for comfort. However, always supervise your cat when they're wearing mittens and remove them if any discomfort is observed.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can Kitten Mittens be used outdoors?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: While Kitten Mittens are primarily designed for indoor use, they can provide some protection for short outdoor trips. For extended outdoor wear, consider our weatherproof outdoor Kitten Mittens collection.
